= Outreach Department

The outreach department is a government department responsible for coordinating the recruitment of individuals from Earth. It is to them that individuals on Earth put forward names to be recruited. This department coordinates with the military to create delegations who will meet with the earthen candidates, as it is not the department themselves who go to earth.